extends layout

block content
  section.gallery-block.cards-gallery
    .container-fluid
      .heading
        h1.title PORTFOLIO - GERFUSA
      .row
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/homepage.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/homepage.png', alt='GERFUSA home page')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Home Page
              p.text-muted.card-text Full window browser width home page look that gives users a peak at what the company does.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/homepage2.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/homepage2.png', alt='GERFUSA how it works')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Home page (continued) - HOW IT WORKS
              p.text-muted.card-text Clicking the "HOW IT WORKS" button shows the ordering a service process from start to delivery.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/services.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/services.png', alt='GERFUSA Services information')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Home page (continued) - SERVICES
              p.text-muted.card-text Clicking on one of the navigation links opens up a detailed description of that service. In the above image there is a detailed description and estimated pricing for Grocery deliveries, Errands service, and Fastfood deliveries.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/login.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/login.png', alt='GERFUSA Login PAGE)
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Home page (continued) - ERRANDS
              p.text-muted.card-text The login page that has an option to sign in with Facebook, Google, and Twitter. Users can also use their GERFUSA created account information if they created their account from the "SIGN UP" page.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/groceries.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/groceries.png', alt='GERFUSA Groceries Order page')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Groceries Page
              p.text-muted.card-text  After logging in a user is redirected to the groceries page where they can start scheduling a delivery by clicking on a chosen store.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/groceries-store.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/groceries-store.png', alt='GERFUSA Groceries Order page')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Groceries Page (continued)
              p.text-muted.card-text  When a user clicks on a chosen store there are shown options the should assist them in completing their order. Depending with the selected store some options will be available or not.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/errands.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/errands.png', alt='GERFUSA Errands page')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Errands Page
              p.text-muted.card-text Clicking on the Errand menu takes you to the errands page where they can start scheduling a delivery by clicking on a chosen errand category.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/fastfood.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/fastfood.png', alt='GERFUSA Login page)
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Fast Food Page
              p.text-muted.card-text Clicking on the Fastfood menu takes you to the errands page where they can start scheduling a delivery by clicking on a chosen fastfood restaurant.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/servicelocations.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/servicelocations.png', alt='GERFUSA Service locations page')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Service Location Page
              p.text-muted.card-text Google Maps API powered page that detects a users location and shows them if there is service in their area or not.
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4
          .card.border-0.transform-on-hover
            a.lightbox(href='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/contactus.png')
              img.card-img-top(src='../images/portifolio/gerfusa/contactus.png', alt='GERFUSA Contact us')
            .card-body
              h6
                a(href='#') Contact Page
              p.text-muted.card-text The contact page provides an option for users to submit information using our form based on a couple of categories. Alternatively they can just see displayed contact information



      #backtohome
        a(href="/") BACK TO HOME
